                  methodType(Object.class, Class.class)
          );
  
          ConstructorGuardedType instance = (ConstructorGuardedType) allocateInstance.invoke(
                  ConstructorGuardedType.class
          );
  
          assertThat(instance.constructorValue()).isZero();
